661
00:48:26,800 --> 00:48:28,100
Get the money from my purse.

662
00:48:28,300 --> 00:48:30,100
I have to work in the darkroom.

663
00:48:30,300 --> 00:48:33,300
It's very important and it can't wait.

664
00:48:33,600 --> 00:48:36,300
