665
00:48:36,500 --> 00:48:38,800
Don't I always? Jesus!

666
00:49:43,500 --> 00:49:45,000
It is, isn't it?

667
00:49:46,000 --> 00:49:47,000
Is this possible?

668
00:49:47,300 --> 00:49:51,800
Here's the aging projection they did
