671
00:49:58,600 --> 00:50:00,500
He's coming back tomorrow.
He ran out of gas.

672
00:50:00,800 --> 00:50:02,100
Where does he live?

673
00:50:02,800 --> 00:50:03,800
Two blocks.

674
00:50:05,000 --> 00:50:06,800
Two blocks from here?

675
00:50:07,200 --> 00:50:08,200
Did he just move here?

676
00:50:08,400 --> 00:50:10,100
I don't know how long...

677
00:50:10,300 --> 00:50:13,300
Kerry knows him from school,
and she's been at Sandburg...

678
00:50:13,600 --> 00:50:15,700
