Good Christ!

679
00:50:18,000 --> 00:50:21,100
He's probably just some kid
who looks like Ben.

680
00:50:21,400 --> 00:50:23,900
-His hair is darker.
-No, you're right.

681
00:50:25,900 --> 00:50:28,700
Let's call Candy.
Then we're going to that house.

682
00:50:29,000 --> 00:50:31,300
It's late at night.
He's sleeping.

683
00:50:31,600 --> 00:50:34,100
We don't even know his last name.

684
00:50:35,700 --> 00:50:38,300
Two blocks from here. I mean...

685
00:50:38,600 --> 00:50:40,100
-When he saw you, did he...
-Nothing.

686
00:50:40,300 --> 00:50:44,700
He had no idea. But he was 3,
