687
00:50:51,200 --> 00:50:52,400
I'm going to call Pop.

688
00:50:52,600 --> 00:50:54,500
Don't tell him.
Not until we know.

689
00:50:54,800 --> 00:50:56,100
No, I just....

690
00:50:56,400 --> 00:50:58,500
I'm not going to work tomorrow.

691
00:51:16,100 --> 00:51:18,200
What were you doing on the porch?

692
00:51:18,700 --> 00:51:20,400
I was watching the sun come up.

693
00:51:20,900 --> 00:51:23,600
-You got a ride?
-Kenny's dad is picking me up.

694
00:51:24,000 --> 00:51:25,000
Finish up.

695
00:51:25,200 --> 00:51:27,800
-I'm riding my bike.
-No, you're not.

696
00:51:28,100 --> 00:51:31,400
