702
00:51:43,400 --> 00:51:44,800
Come on, let's go.

703
00:51:54,300 --> 00:51:55,200
Bye, Mom.

704
00:51:55,900 --> 00:51:57,300
Vincent, wait.

705
00:52:01,300 --> 00:52:02,500
