741
00:54:34,700 --> 00:54:35,600
I think...

742
00:54:35,800 --> 00:54:37,800
She won't be home till after five?

743
00:54:38,100 --> 00:54:38,900
Right.

744
00:54:50,900 --> 00:54:53,200
You saw that picture this morning.

745
00:54:53,700 --> 00:54:55,800
That's why the police are here.

746
00:54:56,000 --> 00:54:58,500
