Can I just go upstairs?

747
00:54:59,800 --> 00:55:01,100
Listen to me.

748
00:55:01,700 --> 00:55:05,300
We think the boy in
that picture is Ben.

749
00:55:05,600 --> 00:55:08,000
The kid in that house on Maple, right?

750
00:55:08,500 --> 00:55:09,700
You saw him?

751
00:55:12,900 --> 00:55:14,100
You saw Ben?

752
00:55:14,400 --> 00:55:17,100
